name: Invictus Flight Jacket
description: Celebrate launch week in iconic style with this commemorative flight jacket featuring a Navy patch on the front and a large Invictus patch on the back. This synthetic leather jacket comes with two front pockets and ribbed waistband and cuffs that guarantee a good fit.
description_cn: 这款纪念飞行夹克以标志性风格来纪念舰队周,其正面有海军标志,背面有大大的舰队周标志.这款合成皮夹克带有两个前袋,腰带和袖口的罗纹设计恰到好处.
